Package gui

Class PickItemsController.IngredientEntry

java.lang.Object
gui.PickItemsController.IngredientEntry
Enclosing class:
PickItemsController
public static class PickItemsController.IngredientEntry extends Object
Represents an ingredient with a selectable checkbox. This inner class manages the ingredient's name and its selected state.
